 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實睇到range rover sport都唔錯，準備過一排去睇下，可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出面啲吸塵機唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前架車就係日日揸加車狗去露營搞到成車毛同泥要成日洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家架車一兩個月吸一次都唔會好難吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會鋪左一層嘢先俾佢地上車<br />\n同埋真係要多d幫佢地梳毛，唔係會好多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我之前個架係絲絨凳，啲毛會攝咗入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢太重所以鋪一層膠係面其實都冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以試下買網上個D dog car seat cover，用左之後最少無咁多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係唔想D狗傷到D皮所以想買架SUV放佢地係行李箱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係用dog seat cover 但因為我隻德牧成36kg ，啲線口位比佢拉爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想放佢係行李箱但放完啲露營同行山gear就冇位比佢，所以要放係後座同比佢申個頭出窗佢會爽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6add55f09f316ffea077ed1f1978f0c1a5faa5f3","tid":296871,"uid":16794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"GLE or Cayenne啦<br />\nAudi小心整撚死你啊"},{"pid":"47b59f7e604ce8d1fbbb487c683b98f1a9f36334","tid":296871,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過Prado 行長途其實好舒服但未坐過GLE行長途所以都心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /