0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/190636_56dda86bdbf3ea8cf12b2e0a9187433e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F190636_56dda86bdbf3ea8cf12b2e0a9187433e.jpg&h=3347a35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢部odyssey嚟，而家換咗Sorento都用到，個籠兩邊有網窗口，後排個冷氣口對到正一正，個籠唔用可以放平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣困住佢地冇位比佢地旭動仲慘，我寧願辛苦少少之後吸塵算"},{"pid":"1f706b6585fb7a0b320b89b49d5de4e19a4af684","tid":296871,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過Prado 行長途其實好舒服但未坐過GLE行長途所以都心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果主打帶狗同road trip 同唔想成日吸塵洗車我覺得Prado最好但如果想要歐洲牌子GLE真係perfect不過要成日清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吸塵呢度10蚊美金洗一次車就有得免費吸，一兩個月去洗一次應該就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實睇到range rover sport都唔錯，準備過一排去睇下，可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出面啲吸塵機唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前架車就係日日揸加車狗去露營搞到成車毛同泥要成日洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家架車一兩個月吸一次都唔會好難吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會鋪左一層嘢先俾佢地上車<br />\n同埋真係要多d幫佢地梳毛，唔係會好多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我之前個架係絲絨凳，啲毛會攝咗入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢太重所以鋪一層膠係面其實都冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以試下買網上個D dog car seat cover，用左之後最少無咁多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係唔想D狗傷到D皮所以想買架SUV放佢地係行李箱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係用dog seat cover 但因為我隻德牧成36kg ，啲線口位比佢拉爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想放佢係行李箱但放完啲露營同行山gear就冇位比佢，所以要放係後座同比佢申個頭出窗佢會爽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係amazon買左呢款<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/110052_7cfbec1740e176e3cc9c513fdd8766b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F110052_7cfbec1740e176e3cc9c513fdd8766b7.jpg&h=14594fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我兩隻狗加埋60幾kg都無咩事，你有興趣可以俾條link你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩 巴打你張櫈拉到咁後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗啦，我依家唔用啦反正佢又唔多係架車到旭同用得多張凳個頭枕個兩條鐵好似會攣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個唔係駕駛座黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e90bb1326377a9d4cabf0a40f6d2594235b46bc","tid":296871,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買部7座, 放低後排d位, 放個狗籠, 我兩隻husky都係咁, 已經少左9成狗毛, 不過小心狗年紀大, suv車身高, 跳上跳落, 關節容易有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7座位既話，GLS有少少over budget，上面有巴打介紹Discovery 5有少少興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗籠就算啦，佢地成世無入過籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d91aa1afae69282820630a8ca17f442aa3d5588","tid":296871,"uid":46838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用緊部mini 5門車隻husky 同西摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMini Countryman? 夠位放咩？你兩隻都算size幾大下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係countryman，正常mini不過5 door<br />\n<br />\n係呀，不過佢地兩個又好乖係後座一人訓一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd6410ccf58dd6a8c5c02343c7edbe63c55c9d4","tid":296871,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"一定係defender <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a6f4d58f0fba08212a07391dc60557ff9dd70e","tid":296871,"uid":77437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"唔考慮model x?"},{"pid":"ac7874c02006b37610671d5d1ad40be6c41def70","tid":296871,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔考慮model x?</blockquote><br />\nmodel x 行road trip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係野外冇電係咪想太陽能發電？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c708f5260468da9a604ff85044e15f87bc2357","tid":296871,"uid":22815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋點解無洗諗Q7？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAudi 車一向保養期內<span style=\"color: red;\">開</span>心，保養期後傷心</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打指教<br />\n<br />\n等我得閒睇下Toyota個款點先，不過如果要歐洲車應該會揀Benz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔好咁講，我都係咁岩最近睇緊SUV同有養狗啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打準備買邊款?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<b